{"tid":1260234,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"腸胃差到仆街冚家產嘅人請入","createTime":"2019-06-26T19:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T19:40:49.000Z","uid":219398,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aea5af11fd999be9f70c7b0b2f6903c05f80940b","tid":1260234,"uid":219398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:30:47.000Z","msg":"屌你從中學時代開始腸胃差，食小小嘢就飽，係飽到從早餐可以頂到晚飯。又好多時食完野之後就肚咕咕聲，又要去痾大屎，但點知都係痾水或者痾左啲氣出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住又個人好虛好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發夢今日圍警總又因為腸胃唔舒服到一個點翻左屋企休養。發現真係好撚困擾。有冇咩方法可以解決。<br />\n利申 乜柒都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372784b73c627ec430fa658e5644796eb2496b2a","tid":1260234,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:32:47.000Z","msg":"食野唔定時 老左就慘<br />\n利申:長食緊胃藥"},{"pid":"288eba359dcb5286c26dc1bbb637a489e8077566","tid":1260234,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:34:36.000Z","msg":"食清淡啲一排先"},{"pid":"14c286d28bb07487421b356266edbe67c8c31559","tid":1260234,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"372784b73c627ec430fa658e5644796eb2496b2a","tid":1260234,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:32:47.000Z","msg":"食野唔定時 老左就慘<br />\n利申:長食緊胃藥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點算好"},{"pid":"1f1805d8c9954db357555d20705762bb1b2a750d","tid":1260234,"uid":219398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:40:49.000Z","msg":"而家每日都做流肛華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji